<plot>It is the first of the series. As an international composer, Gabriel Yared has written the original score of numerous films, including "Betty Blue" by Jean-Jacques Beineix, "Camille Claudel" by Bruno Nuytten, "The Lover" by Jean-Jacques Annaud, "The English Patient", "Cold Mountain", "The Talented Mister Ripley" and "Breaking &amp; Entering" by Anthony Minghella. "In the Tracks of Gabriel Yared" brings the audience into the creative process of his film scores through interviews with collaborative personalities like Jean-Hugues Anglade and Jean-Jacques Annaud, from the very personal beginning to the movie theatre projectors.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?263567</url></doc>
